## 🏗️ Code Structure Patterns

### Web Frontend (Next.js) - App Router Pattern

```
packages/3-web/
├── src/
│   ├── app/                            # Next.js App Router
│   │   ├── layout.tsx                  # Root layout (providers, error boundaries)
│   │   ├── page.tsx                    # Home page (Storefront)
│   │   ├── providers.tsx                # Context providers (QueryClient, etc.)
│   │   │
│   │   └── 📁 (main)/                  # Main route group
│   │       ├── 📁 browse/              # Browse & Discovery
│   │       ├── 📁 rankings/           # Rankings
│   │       ├── 📁 feed/               # Social Feed
│   │       ├── 📁 groups/             # Social Groups
│   │       ├── 📁 library/            # Library & Bookshelf
│   │       ├── 📁 reader/             # Reader Interface
│   │       ├── 📁 wallet/            # Wallet & Payments
│   │       ├── 📁 subscriptions/      # Subscriptions
│   │       └── 📁 notifications/      # Notifications
│   │
│   ├── components/                     # React components (Atomic Design)
│   │   ├── ui/                         # Atoms (shadcn/ui primitives)
